CORAM :  HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE PAMIDIGHANTAM SRI NARASIMHA
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE R. MAHADEVAN
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) :Mr. R. Nedumbaran, Sr. Adv.                     
                   Mr. Samir Arunkumar Vaidya, Adv.
                   Mr. V. Balaji, Adv. 
                   Mr. Anand Dilip Landge, AOR
                                      
For Respondent(s) :Mr. Abhishek Chandra Mishra , AOR
                   
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
1.Permission to file the Special Leave Petition is granted.
2.Issue notice returnable in two weeks.
3.Mr. Abhishek Chandra Mishra, learned AOR accepts notice on
1 of 2 Diary No(s). 34694/2025
behalf of the respondent(s) on caveat.
4.In the meantime, operation of the impugned order shall remain 
stayed.
(KAPIL TANDON)                                  (NIDHI WASON)
